### Pengujian Titik Akhir API Autentikasi

# 1. Mendaftarkan Pengguna Baru
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Jikasa",
  "email": "jikasa@gmail.com",
  "password": "123123"
}

###

# 2. Masuk Pengguna (Login)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jikasa@gmail.com",
  "password": "123123"
}

###

# 3. Keluar Pengguna (Logout)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJqaWthc2FAZ21haWwuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzczMTg1ODYwLCJleHAiOjE3NzMyNzIyNjB9.w9zbmGjom3tHAA_cYXmsiBiuJjR4KrBUpl5u-ER1lKw
